text: Chabaud may refer to: ==People== *Alain Chabaud (1923-2013), French parasitologist. *Auguste Chabaud (1882-1955), French painter and sculptor. *Jaime Chabaud (born 1966), Mexican playwright. *Louis-Félix Chabaud (1824-1902), French sculptor and medallist. *Sébastien Chabaud (born 1977), French football player.
